---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Contact Us
description: Get in touch with OneDevKit. Send us feedback, suggestions, or questions about our free online developer tools.
keywords: contact onedevkit, feedback, support, suggestions, developer tools
permalink: /contact/
---
{% block schema %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.url }}/"},
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Contact", "item": "{{ site.url }}/contact/"}
  ]
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ContactPage",
  "name": "Contact {{ site.name }}",
  "description": "{{ description }}",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}/contact/",
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "{{ site.name }}",
    "url": "{{ site.url }}",
    "contactPoint": {"@type": "ContactPoint", "contactType": "customer support", "email": "{{ site.email }}"}
  }
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{% block head %}
<style>
  .lead { font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; }
  .contact-methods { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  .contact-card { background: var(--bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
  .contact-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; margin: 0 auto 1rem; color: var(--primary); }
  .contact-icon svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
  .contact-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .contact-card p { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .contact-link { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.125rem; }
  .contact-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .contact-topics { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .contact-topics li { padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
  .contact-topics li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .contact-topics strong { color: var(--text-primary); }
</style>
{% endblock %}

<h1>Contact Us</h1>

<section class="content-section">
  <p class="lead">We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have feedback, suggestions for new tools, found a bug, or just want to say hello, we're here to listen.</p>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
  <div class="contact-methods">
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div class="contact-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Email</h3>
      <p>For general inquiries, feedback, or support:</p>
      <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" class="contact-link">{{ site.email }}</a>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div class="contact-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>X (Twitter)</h3>
      <p>Follow us for updates and quick support:</p>
      <a href="https://x.com/{{ site.twitter | replace('@', '') }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link">{{ site.twitter }}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>What We'd Love to Hear</h2>
  <ul class="contact-topics">
    <li><strong>Tool Suggestions:</strong> Have an idea for a new developer tool? We're always looking to expand our toolkit.</li>
    <li><strong>Bug Reports:</strong> Found something that doesn't work correctly? Let us know and we'll fix it.</li>
    <li><strong>Feature Requests:</strong> Want to see improvements to existing tools? Tell us how we can make them better.</li>
    <li><strong>General Feedback:</strong> Love our tools? Have constructive criticism? We appreciate all feedback.</li>
    <li><strong>Partnership Inquiries:</strong> Interested in collaborating? Get in touch!</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>Response Time</h2>
  <p>We're a small team, but we try to respond to all messages within 2-3 business days. For bug reports, we'll prioritize based on severity and impact.</p>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>Before You Reach Out</h2>
  <p>You might find answers to common questions in these resources:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/about/">About OneDevKit</a> - Learn about our mission and how our tools work</li>
    <li><a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> - Understand how we handle data</li>
    <li><a href="/terms/">Terms of Service</a> - Read our terms and conditions</li>
  </ul>
</section>
